(343, 1, '2014-06-26 15:34:49', '2014-06-26 15:34:49', 'Flushing bar is a piece of equipment that is mounted on mowing machines. These simple devices create noise and vibrations that alert any species that may be near the equipment to get out of the way.\r\n\r\nFlushing bars are available to farmers through Ducks Unlimited Canada. To get a flushing bar, you can get in touch with DUC in Amherst, NS at <a href="mailto:du_amherst@ducks.ca">du_amherst@ducks.ca</a>, or toll free at: 1-866-903-8257', 'Flushing Bars', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'flushing-bars', '', '', '2014-06-26 15:34:49', '2014-06-26 15:34:49', '', 317, 'http://localhost/farming/?page_id=343', 0, 'page', '', 0),
